name: (G)I-DLE Miyeon
description:
If you like my LoRAs please consider to support me by buying me a coffee here so I can make a new LoRA faster. I do open commissions there too if you want to make your own custom LoRA.

Don't forget to include trigger word: gidlemiyeon

Best checkpoints/models to use with this: VisionGen

Maybe works good with other models too but I haven't tried it yet so let me know.

Use this wisely. I don't responsible for anything you generated with this LoRA.

modelVersions.name: (G)I-DLE Miyeon - v1
modelVersions.description:
Trained on latest version of Linaqruf's colab using 30 images with HassanBlend 1.4 as its base model.

Best at close-up, pose will be repetitive at some seeds and prompts because its dataset have many similar pose, but it can be solved with Controlnet, the face similarity will be decrease though.
